function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(ID_MAGS)
	Hydra.QActorUnsheath(ID_MAGS)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_MAGS)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(ID_MAGS)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_POSSESSED)
	
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_MAGS_01, ID_POSSESSED)
	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_POSSESSED, 1)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_POSSESSED, CONVO_MAGS_01)
	Hydra.QActorSetTeam(ID_POSSESSED, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	idPriest = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_Inheritance_01_Priest")
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_PRIEST)
	
	--Deserter Movement
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_PRIEST) then	
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_PRIEST, LOC_PRIEST, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_PRIEST, ID_PRIEST)
	end
end
